sentence: Welcome to the latest installment of community stock picks and overview of some of the most-read stories of the week.
We're taking a look at stocks chosen by members of the Nasdaq.com community from June 19 - 25.

Bullish Stocks: Here's What You Said:

Oasmia Pharmaceutical (OASM): Time to buy again!
One of the best growth stories available in the market!
Wells Fargo (WFC): True to conservative basket investing.
They show diversity and meet more standards for consistent growth.
Annaly Capital Management (NLY): Owned it for 5 years now.
Held 10% plus dividend and now Oxford Club has ranked it as a buy.
FMC Corporation (FMC): Lithium is on the rise, and FMC is one of the largest producers.
Salesforce (CRM): The merger between Microsoft and LinkedIn will complement Salesforce and help it grow.
